{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "PredictIQ SLO Dashboard",
    "tags": ["slo", "reliability", "error-budget"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "refresh": "30s",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "SLO Compliance Overview",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "slo:api_availability:success_rate",
            "legendFormat": "API Availability"
          },
          {
            "expr": "slo:api_latency_p95:success_rate * 100",
            "legendFormat": "API Latency P95"
          },
          {
            "expr": "slo:cache_availability:success_rate",
            "legendFormat": "Cache Availability"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "value": 0, "color": "red" },
                { "value": 95, "color": "yellow" },
                { "value": 99, "color": "green" }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Error Budget Remaining",
        "type": "gauge",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "slo:api_availability:error_budget_remaining",
            "legendFormat": "API Availability"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                { "value": 0, "color": "red" },
                { "value": 10, "color": "orange" },
                { "value": 25, "color": "yellow" },
                { "value": 50, "color": "green" }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "Burn Rate (1h/6h/24h)",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "slo:api_availability:burn_rate_1h",
            "legendFormat": "1h burn rate"
          },
          {
            "expr": "slo:api_availability:burn_rate_6h",
            "legendFormat": "6h burn rate"
          },
          {
            "expr": "slo:api_availability:burn_rate_24h",
            "legendFormat": "24h burn rate"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {
            "label": "Burn Rate (x)",
            "format": "short"
          }
        ],
        "alert": {
          "conditions": [
            {
              "evaluator": {
                "params": [14.4],
                "type": "gt"
              },
              "operator": {
                "type": "and"
              },
              "query": {
                "params": ["A", "5m", "now"]
              },
              "reducer": {
                "params": [],
                "type": "avg"
              },
              "type": "query"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Fast Burn Alert"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "API Request Success Rate",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{status=~\"2..|3..\"}[5m])) / sum(rate(http_requests_total[5m])) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "Success Rate"
          },
          {
            "expr": "99.9",
            "legendFormat": "SLO Target"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {
            "label": "Success Rate (%)",
            "format": "percent",
            "min": 99,
            "max": 100
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "title": "API Latency P95/P99",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le)) * 1000",
            "legendFormat": "P95 Latency"
          },
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le)) * 1000",
            "legendFormat": "P99 Latency"
          },
          {
            "expr": "200",
            "legendFormat": "P95 Target"
          },
          {
            "expr": "500",
            "legendFormat": "P99 Target"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {
            "label": "Latency (ms)",
            "format": "ms"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "title": "Error Budget Burn Down",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "slo:api_availability:error_budget_remaining",
            "legendFormat": "Budget Remaining"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {
            "label": "Budget Remaining (%)",
            "format": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 7,
        "title": "SLO Violations (Last 7 Days)",
        "type": "table",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "ALERTS{alertname=~\"SLO.*\"}",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 8,
        "title": "Database Query Latency P95",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(db_query_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le)) * 1000",
            "legendFormat": "P95 Query Latency"
          },
          {
            "expr": "50",
            "legendFormat": "Target"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {
            "label": "Latency (ms)",
            "format": "ms"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 9,
        "title": "Cache Hit Rate",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate(redis_commands_total{status=\"hit\"}[5m])) / sum(rate(redis_commands_total[5m])) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "Hit Rate"
          },
          {
            "expr": "80",
            "legendFormat": "Target"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {
            "label": "Hit Rate (%)",
            "format": "percent"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 10,
        "title": "Monthly Error Budget Policy",
        "type": "text",
        "content": "## Error Budget Policy\n\n- **100% remaining**: Normal operations\n- **50% remaining**: Review recent changes\n- **25% remaining**: Freeze non-critical deployments\n- **10% remaining**: Freeze all deployments\n- **0% remaining**: Emergency - rollback and incident response\n\n### Burn Rate Thresholds\n\n- **Fast Burn (14.4x)**: Exhausts budget in 2 days → Critical alert\n- **Slow Burn (6.0x)**: Exhausts budget in 5 days → Warning alert"
      }
    ],
      },
      {
        "id": 11,
        "title": "Database Query Latency P50/P95/P99",
        "type": "graph",
        "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(db_query_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le)) * 1000",
            "legendFormat": "P50 Latency",
            "refId": "A"
          },
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(db_query_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le)) * 1000",
            "legendFormat": "P95 Latency",
            "refId": "B"
          },
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(db_query_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le)) * 1000",
            "legendFormat": "P99 Latency",
            "refId": "C"
          },
          {
            "expr": "500",
            "legendFormat": "P95 Alert Threshold",
            "refId": "D"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {
            "label": "Latency (ms)",
            "format": "ms"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "time": {
      "from": "now-7d",
      "to": "now"
    }
  }
}
    "time": {
      "from": "now-7d",
      "to": "now"
    }
  }
}